snippet.textDisplay: Am I the only one who thinks this  is shite? I know artists appropriate others work to create something unique but I find Elizabeth's too obvious..Nenah Cherry and Amy Winehouse (obviously) spring to mind instantly but if you stop and think about the lyrics they're clunky and cliched. I think she's lost her way a bit. Ultaviolence was incredibly creative, stunning. I am not a hater so before anyone accuses me of that.
